  "name": "DB LoadTypeName",
  "description": " VM_IF_CONST .EQ,  VAR_TEMP3, 1, Type1, 0\n VM_IF_CONST .EQ,  VAR_TEMP3, 2, Type2, 0\n VM_IF_CONST .EQ,  VAR_TEMP3, 3, Type3, 0\nVM_IF_CONST .EQ,  VAR_TEMP3, 4, Type4, 0\n VM_IF_CONST .EQ,  VAR_TEMP3, 5, Type5, 0\n VM_IF_CONST .EQ,  VAR_TEMP3, 6, Type6, 0\n VM_IF_CONST .EQ,  VAR_TEMP3, 7, Type7, 0\n VM_JUMP AetherType\n\nType1:\n VM_SET_CONST VAR_Wordy1, \"W\"\nVM_SET_CONST VAR_Wordy2, \"o\"\nVM_SET_CONST VAR_Wordy3, \"o\"\nVM_SET_CONST VAR_Wordy4, \"d\"\nVM_SET_CONST VAR_Wordy5, 0\nVM_SET_CONST VAR_Wordy6, 0\n\n1 = wood\nelectroweak\nwater\nfire\nmetal\nstrong\nspacetime = 7\nelse aether = 0\n\nusing a switch, but alternatively could use code similar to the above",
